name: The Trees and The Life #001-Kambera
description:
As far as your eyes can see, Kambera lies kilometers of nothing but savanna. Wind from the north blows hot air through the gap of grass, they're singing once in a while. Mr. Sun was covered by the cloud that day otherwise, those Acacia trees would have been packed by the horses. 

The Trees and The Life is 10-Photo-Based-NFT Collection made by Danar Tri Atmojo. As the first-ever collection made, Danar dedicated these NFT's to mother nature as we move towards the new era of digitalization using Tezos blockchain as #CleanNFTs.
